The paper focuses on tracking and predicting behaviors of surrounding objects, which is a key prerequisite for autonomous vehicles. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of learning-based models for prediction, which suggests that it could also belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also discusses decision making and motion planning, which are topics commonly associated with Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-categories.
